'''Suovetaurilius''', also known as Suet, was the page of [[Georgius]], who was the son of [[Farmer Giles]], who became the king of the [[Little Kingdom]].<ref>[[J.R.R. Tolkien]], ''[[Farmer Giles of Ham]]'', Foreword</ref>
